data.description: Welcome home to this PREINSPECTED beauty located in Little Italy that is MOVE IN READY! Updated kitchen with quartz and butcher block oversized island, complemented by stainless steel appliances. Updated plumbing and electrical. AC & Furnace replaced in 2021. Bathroom updates include marble countertop vanities. All appliances stay including washer and dryer. The neighborhood's location of Little Italy and near Little Bohemia, and the Old Market provides a wonderful mix of cultural influences and opportunities for entertainment and dining. The proximity to Dahlman Park, complete with its playground, basketball courts, and tennis courts, offers great outdoor leisure activities right at your doorstep. AMA
